const BODIES={ Day_0:(fn,co,sig,cl)=>'<p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Hi '+fn+',</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">I was reviewing '+co+' and thought Example Company could be relevant to your team.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Example Company helps service organizations report rental payment history to the credit bureaus, giving customers credit for their largest monthly payment while helping operators improve customer engagement, collections, and retention.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Would you be open to a brief 15-minute conversation to see if this could be a fit for your organization?</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Best regards,</p>'+sig.replace('CALENDLY_PLACEHOLDER',cl), Day_5:(fn,sig,cl)=>'<p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Hi '+fn+',</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">I wanted to follow up on my previous note.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Many service organizations initially look at Example Company as a customers benefit, but they also see value through improved payment behavior, stronger customer engagement, and additional differentiation for owners and customers.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Is account reporting something your team has evaluated?</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Best,</p>'+sig.replace('CALENDLY_PLACEHOLDER',cl), Day_14:(fn,sig,cl)=>"<p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Hi "+fn+",</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">One of the reasons our clients implement Example Company is because rent is often a customers's largest monthly expense, yet historically it has not helped build credit.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">By reporting rental payments, property managers can offer a meaningful customers benefit while creating additional value for customers, owners, and the management company.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">I would be happy to share how other service organizations are implementing the program.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Would next week work for a brief conversation?</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Best,</p>"+sig.replace('CALENDLY_PLACEHOLDER',cl), Day_21:(fn,sig,cl)=>'<p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Hi '+fn+',</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">I wanted to close the loop on my previous notes.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Example Company helps service organizations report rental payment history to the credit bureaus, giving customers credit for their largest monthly payment while helping operators improve customer engagement, collections, and retention.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">If this is something your team may want to explore, I would be happy to schedule a brief 15-minute conversation.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">If now is not the right time, no worries at all.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px 0; line-height:1.4;">Best regards,</p>'+sig.replace('CALENDLY_PLACEHOLDER',cl) };
